Description: The Flight into Egypt: Holy Family with St Joseph pointing to left, Virgin at his side with Child in her arms and looking at angel walking ahead of her and offering her a rose Engraving
Producer name: Print made by: François de Poilly I
Curator's comments: Intermediary state between II and III: finished proof, but before the coat of arms and the inscriptions in the margin.
Bibliographic references: Lothe 1994 / L'Oeuvre Gravé de François et Nicolas de Poilly (313.II/III)
Acquisition name: Bequeathed by: Clayton Mordaunt Cracherode (with monogram (L.607) and date 1791)
